### Local tooling (machine-specific, not source) ###
# tools/ is where a local JDK gets dropped — but gen_resources.py IS source: it generates
# every blockstate, model, loot table, tag and recipe under src/main/resources. Keep it.
/tools/*
!/tools/gen_resources.py

